{
  "stem": "6258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, it become these things with cleaning the streets, and cleaning from snow, and this and that, all kind of this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then suddenly, it was first in June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was the great deportation, when for about a week, the Germans rounded the ghetto and were taking--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "June of '41 or '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me check with my diary, because we just talk and talk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] I think 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was June.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- first, it was in June, and another one was in October.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the same year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, we just simply couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, at least, I couldn't understand, and I couldn't comprehend how it comes that suddenly people are here, and then they are taken and they disappear.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody knows where they are going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was said that they are going to the east, to Russia to work, or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you never heard about these people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when there were coming such strange things, that they were-- they were-- they were being taken to gas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were massacres and this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, it's also something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every ghetto was so isolated that we absolutely had no idea what was going on in the world, so what was going on in other towns, even in another-- in other villages.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were like uniquely for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no communication, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after this June terrible, well, very bad deportation-- or Aussiedlung, as the German call it-- then there was-- it was said that we all have to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody has to work, and we went to forced jobs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some people didn't wanted to go outside of the ghetto, because they were the very menial jobs.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
